svg.text: Niǔyuē lí wǒmen zhèr yuǎn ma?
纽约离我们这儿很远/不远/很近。
Niǔyuē lí wǒmen zhèr hěn yuǎn/bù yuǎn/hěn jìn.
In pairs, role-play a friend coming to visit your school and make suggestions for showing him/
her around. Pick a place and an activity depicted below, and use the “
+ place + action” patterns to discuss possible itineraries, e.g.:
我们到公园去滑冰，好吗？/
Wǒmen dào gōngyuán qù huá bīng, hǎo ma?/Wǒmen qù gōngyuán huá bīng, hǎo ma?
